        "text_block_YrcCYz": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Flattering Bikini Bottoms for Every Body and Every Occassion",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": true,
            "text": "<p>Finding the perfect bikini bottom is about more than coverage — it’s about confidence. Our collection brings together sleek high waisted bikini bottoms, playful low rise bikini bottoms, and ultra-soft seamless bikini bottoms, all crafted from luxurious Italian recycled fabric that feels as good as it looks.</p><p>Every pair is thoughtfully cut to flatter the female form while staying secure through surf, swim, and sun. Designed for women who live for the water, these sustainable bikini bottoms combine style and substance in equal measure.</p><p>Our signature fabrics offer UPF 50+ sun protection, chlorine and salt resistance, and a sculpting stretch that smooths and supports without digging in. Whether you choose the sleek lines of a seamless bikini bottom, the retro vibe of a high waisted cut, or the barely-there freedom of a string bikini bottom, you’ll feel comfortable, confident, and completely yourself.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        }
