    "image_with_text_4MJHr7": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/women-rash-guard-the-sumba-crop-rash-vest-ocean-soul-bali-6.webp",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Find Your Perfect Fit",
        "text": "<h4><strong>High Waisted Bikini Bottoms</strong></h4><p>Our <a href=\"/collections/high-waisted-bikini\" title=\"High Waisted Bikini\">high waisted bikini bottoms</a> are a customer favourite for a reason. They sculpt and smooth the waist, offer extra tummy support, and create a timeless hourglass shape. The higher cut elongates the legs while offering secure coverage — ideal for active days in the water or poolside lounging.</p><p>Sculpting panels that flatter without feeling restrictive<br/></p><p>Double-lined for support and opacity<br/></p><p>Designed to stay put through every wave</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_XmjLmY": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/low-rise-bikini-bottom-the-banyak-bikini-bottom-ocean-soul-bali-9.webp",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Low Rise Bikini Bottoms",
        "text": "<p>Prefer a minimalist fit? Our <a href=\"/collections/low-rise-bikini\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Low Rise Bikini\">low rise bikini bottoms</a> sit comfortably on the hips for a modern, effortless look. Perfect for tanning and light surf, they offer freedom of movement without compromising style.</p><p>Soft, stretchy fabric that moves with you<br/></p><p>Clean, contoured lines for a flattering fit<br/></p><p>Minimal coverage with maximum confidence</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_qmMtBN": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Aceh_bikini_bottom_Bali_bikini_top_green.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Seamless Bikini Bottoms",
        "text": "<p>If comfort is key, our <a href=\"/collections/seamless-bikinis\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Seamless Bikinis & Two Pieces\">seamless bikini bottoms</a> are a dream. No stitching, no pinching — just a smooth, second-skin feel that sculpts beautifully. Ideal for long beach days or layering under a wetsuit, they embody our commitment to luxury you can feel.</p><p>Seamless construction for all-day comfort<br/></p><p>Soft, recycled Italian fabric that lasts<br/></p><p>UPF 50+ protection and fade resistance</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_zATp6G": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Triangle_string_bikini_green.png",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "String Bikini Bottoms",
        "text": "<p>For those who love adjustability and freedom, our <a href=\"/collections/string-bikini\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"String Bikini\">string bikini bottoms</a> feature tie sides for a custom fit that flatters every shape. These are made for sun-seekers who like a little less coverage and a lot of style.</p><p>Adjustable ties for the perfect fit<br/></p><p>Double-lined for confidence and comfort<br/></p><p>Minimal design that pairs effortlessly with any top</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
